{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDAyMTQwNTIy", "number": 427, "title": "Fix Exoplayer Caching", "bodyText": "It turns out Picasso was actually using OkHttp through reflection. It seems that without it, Picasso was setting up some crazy caching to disk behavior on the default HTTP stack. This caused streams played by Exoplayer to be cached to disk when we updated Exoplayer from 2.10.6 to 2.11.3.\n\nFixes #417", "createdAt": "2020-04-11T04:54:42Z", "url": "https://github.com/jellyfin/jellyfin-androidtv/pull/427", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "c40fa3eb61e851c6259e6db66fbbc06bc206b4e8"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-04-13T17:24:21Z", "author": {"login": "thornbill"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 5, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcWeIvfgH2gAyNDAyMTQwNTIyOjRiMzgwNTE1M2IwN2UwOTJmMGE4MzgwNjc0Yjg1ZWU3YTE0ZWUxMzY=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcXSR8jAFqTM5MjI5NDY4Nw==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "4b3805153b07e092f0a8380674b85ee7a14ee136", "author": {"user": {"login": "thornbill", "name": "Bill Thornton"}}, "url": "https://github.com/jellyfin/jellyfin-androidtv/commit/4b3805153b07e092f0a8380674b85ee7a14ee136", "committedDate": "2020-04-11T04:39:07Z", "message": "Revert \"Remove (unused) okhttp dependency\"\n\nThis reverts commit 1a4f9d29d32212f440843cea6727d4ace19c0fe1."}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "0863abd93ef6d4fa76add66d506fbe30b0dc6846", "author": {"user": {"login": "thornbill", "name": "Bill Thornton"}}, "url": "https://github.com/jellyfin/jellyfin-androidtv/commit/0863abd93ef6d4fa76add66d506fbe30b0dc6846", "committedDate": "2020-04-11T04:44:00Z", "message": "Add note on why okhttp is needed"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3MzkxNzQ2MDky", "url": "https://github.com/jellyfin/jellyfin-androidtv/pull/427#pullrequestreview-391746092", "createdA